    DEF  INPUT PARAM par_dsorigip AS CHAR                           NO-UNDO.
	DEF  INPUT PARAM par_flmobile AS LOGI                           NO-UNDO.
    DEF  INPUT PARAM par_flgerlog AS LOGI                           NO-UNDO.
        
